#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:38
msgid "The Armature Object"
msgstr "The Armature Object 骨架物体"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:40
msgid "As you can see, an armature is like any other object type in Blender:"
msgstr "正如你所看到的, 骨架物体像Blender 的其它物体类型:"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:42
msgid "It has a center, a position, a rotation and a scale factor."
msgstr "它有一个中心,位置、 旋转、缩放属性。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:43
msgid "It has an Object Data data-block, that can be edited in *Edit Mode*."
msgstr "有物体数据块, 所以能够在 *编辑模式（Edit mode ）* 中被编辑."

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:44
msgid ""
"It can be linked to other scenes, and the same armature data can be reused on "
"multiple objects."
msgstr "它可以被连结到其它场景, 同样的骨架数据可以被多个物体使用。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:45
msgid ""
"All animation you do in *Object Mode* is only working on the whole object, not "
"the armature's bones (use the *Pose Mode* to do this)."
msgstr ""
"在 *物体模式（Object mode）* 下所有的动画仅仅工作在整个物体的,而不是骨架的骨骼 "
"(在 *姿势模式下（Pose mode）* 可以做到这点)。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:48
msgid ""
"As armatures are designed to be posed, either for a static or animated scene, "
"they have a specific state, called \"rest position\". This is the armature's "
"default \"shape\", the default position/rotation/scale of its bones, as set in "
"*Edit Mode*."
msgstr ""
"骨架是为姿势设计的, 无论是静态或动态场景, 它们有一个特别的姿态叫 “重置位置（rest "
"position）”. 这个骨骼有默认的“形状”, 默认的位置/旋转/缩放, 在 *编辑模式* 可以设置"
"改变它们。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/introduction.rst:52
msgid ""
"In *Edit Mode*, you will always see your armature in rest position, whereas in "
"*Object Mode* and *Pose Mode*, you usually get the current \"pose\" of the "
"armature (unless you enable the *Rest Position* button of the *Armature* panel)."
msgstr ""
"在 *编辑模式（Edit mode）*， 你总是看到骨架在重置位置（rest position）, 而在 *对"
"象Object* 和 *姿势Pose模式*, 你通常得到当前的骨架“姿势”(除非你启用了 *骨架"
"（Armature）* 面板的 *重置位置（rest position）* 按钮)。"

